5thLevelRangerSpells.Name: Commune with Nature
5thLevelRangerSpells.Description: You briefly become one with nature and gain knowledge of the surrounding territory.

5thLevelRangerSpells.Name: Tree Stride
5thLevelRangerSpells.Description: You gain the ability to enter a tree and move from inside it to inside another tree of the same kind within 500 feet.
